|ID|OPERATOR          |NAME |EST. ROWS|COST|
--------------------------------------------
|0 |DISTRIBUTED INSERT|     |1        |59  |
|1 | SUBPLAN SCAN     |VIEW1|1        |46  |
|2 |  TABLE SCAN      |tt1  |1        |46  |
============================================

Outputs & filters: 
-------------------------------------
  0 - output(nil), filter(nil), 
      columns([{tt2: ({tt2: (tt2.__pk_increment, tt2.a)})}]), partitions(p0), 
      column_values([column_conv(BIGINT UNSIGNED,PS:(-1,-1),NOT NULL,tt2.__pk_increment.nextval())], [column_conv(INT,PS:(11,0),NULL,VIEW1.a)])
  1 - output([VIEW1.a]), filter(nil), 
      access([VIEW1.a])
  2 - output([tt1.a]), filter(nil), 
      access([tt1.a]), partitions(p0)

// switch tt1 to backup server
insert into tt2 select * from tt1;
insert into tt2 select * from tt1;

explain insert into tt2 select * from tt1;
